targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.query:
SELECT
    $timeSeries as t,
    avg(metric_values[indexOf(metric_names, 'ampHours')]) AS "C400"
FROM $table
WHERE
    $timeFilter
    AND indexOf(metric_names, 'ampHours') > 0
    AND instance = 'C400'
GROUP BY t
ORDER BY t
targets.rawQuery: SELECT     (intDiv(toUInt32(dt), 120) * 120) * 1000 as t,     avg(metric_values[indexOf(metric_names, 'sensorVoltage')]) AS "S216" FROM default.measurements WHERE     dt >= toDateTime(1588533223)     AND instance = 'S216' GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
